snippet: Boeing Co said on Monday that regulators have certified the 787-9 Dreamliner, clearing the way for the new, stretched jet's on-time arrival to its first customer, Air New Zealand, possibly later this month....

headline.print_headline: Boeing 787-9 Dreamliner Cleared for On-Time Delivery
headline.main: Boeing 787-9 Dreamliner Cleared for On-Time Delivery

lead_paragraph: Boeing Co said on Monday that regulators have certified the 787-9 Dreamliner, clearing the way for the new, stretched jet's on-time arrival to its first customer, Air New Zealand, possibly later this month.
